review_text: Excellent experience with Lisa as our guide through the daunting mortgage loan process. She was patient, very approachable and got back to us immediately whenever we had any questions. We like banking with our local community bank!

This bank was a community bank!  Helping people to keep their money in the community.  Lately this bank is exploiting its customers with unfair fees.
Not communicating important situations properly by leaving messages on house answering machines not trying to contacting the person on their CELL phone. After 17 years I will be changing my Bank!!!
